      "content": "When aiming for \"effortless competence,\" the goal is to look like you've mastered the standard corporate aesthetic. For those with textured hair, sleek, well-maintained styles that are pulled back or kept very tidy are best to avoid any visual distraction. Similarly, head coverings should be chosen in professional, solid colors that blend seamlessly with the overall conservative attire. The focus should always be on the message, not the style.",
